{"type":null,"faqId":38987,"title":"如何更新手环版本和APP版本？","answer":"<p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;text-indent:24.0pt;\nline-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\n\">升级前，请确保手环和手机通过蓝牙正常连接。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;text-indent:24.0pt;\nline-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\n\">更新手环版本：在</span><span style=\"\nfont-family:'Arial','sans-serif'\">APP</span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">中点击左上角设置图标，点击“更新荣耀手环</span><span style=\"font-family:'Arial','sans-serif'\"> zero”</span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">，手环将会检测版本信息并更新。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;text-align:center;text-indent:24.0pt;\nline-height:normal\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';layout-grid-mode:\nboth;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150908084807170001.png\" style=\"width:226.5pt;height:137.25pt\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;text-indent:24.0pt;\nline-height:normal\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;text-indent:24.0pt;\nline-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\n\">更新</span><span style=\"font-family:\n'Arial','sans-serif'\">APP</span><span style=\"\nfont-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">版本：在</span><span style=\"font-family:'Arial','sans-serif'\">APP</span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">中点击右上角小人图标，点击“关于</span><span style=\"font-family:'Arial','sans-serif'\">”-</span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">“</span><span style=\"font-family:'Arial','sans-serif'\">App</span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">版本更新”，当手机显示“更新</span><span style=\"font-family:'Arial','sans-serif'\">...”</span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">时，即可检测</span><span style=\"font-family:'Arial','sans-serif'\">APP</span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">版本信息并更新。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;text-indent:24.0pt;\nline-height:normal\"><span style=\"\nfont-family:'Arial','sans-serif';layout-grid-mode:both;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150908084807283002.png\" style=\"width:387pt;height:146.25pt\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;line-height:normal;\ntext-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other\"><b><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">说明：</span></b></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;line-height:normal;\ntext-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other\"><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">更新时，手环会自动断开蓝牙，请您耐心等待直至升级结束。</span></p>\n<br>\n</p>","faqTypeId":212,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"4297","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1441673017000,"seriesProductName":"B0-Honor","visitedTimes":1